<s> This touches on something that's been on my mind for a while.  </s>
<s> If a query is "a string of information to be interpreted by the resource," isn't it the case that a URI with a query refers to a resource, rather than just identifies one?  </s>
<s> E.g., http://www.example.com/foo?bar=baz is a reference to the resource http://www.example.com/foo .  </s>
<s> I.e., shouldn't the definition of URI-Reference (rather than URI)  </s>
