<s> Mark Nottingham  </s>
<s> Definitions are often choosen on their practical value, rather than on philosophical considerations.  </s>
<s> In this case, the URI is what you (e.g.) send to the server, the URI Reference is what you (e.g.) put into an attribute.  </s>
